imdb.title: 30 Vies
plot: The titular "30 lives" of this daily serial drama are those of a high school class, seen through the eyes of the lead character: their teacher. Viewers share in every challenge faced, every life lesson learned. Journeying into the private lives of students and tackling such topical themes as street violence, bullying and rising dropout rates, 30 vies is a compelling, inspiring social drama.
